data.description: This affordable Florida home is the perfect place to call home. Completely fenced in rear yard that backs up to a conservation/preserve area with lots of privacy. Professionally installed above ground pool added for those warm summer days. Loaded with features this 3 bedroom 2 bath spacious 1655 square foot home it the perfect size and design. Open Kitchen will lots of storage & counter space. Ceiling fans throughout. With high ceilings throughout the kitchen/dining/living area this home offers and nice open feel.  Ashby Landing is an excellent community in St. Augustine located off SR 207, just a small walk to the Epic Movie Theatre. Close to town, shopping, excellent schools, all this and more plus a short 10 minute drive to St Augustine Beach and the Historic Downtown St Augustine. Centrally located to all St Augustine has to offer. Don't let this one slip away! Energy Efficient air conditioning and heating system, double pane windows, Energy efficient water heater, and PVC plumbing are just a few of the long list of features offered. See attached floor plan and list of features.
